The paper proposes a learning approach for a personal robot to place multiple objects in a scene, which involves designing appropriate features and using a graphical model to encode various properties. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-categories.
